<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<title>Crew Invitation Cancelled - iGreenMon</title>
	</head>

	<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 2rem; color: #333">
		<h2>Your Crew Invitation Has Been Cancelled</h2>
		<p>Hi <%= invitee %>,</p>
		<p>
			We wanted to let you know that <strong><%= inviter %></strong> has
			cancelled their invitation for you to join the greenhouse
			<strong><%= greenhouse %></strong>.
		</p>
		<p>
			This means you will no longer be able to accept this invitation. If
			you believe this was a mistake, you can reach out to <%= inviter %>
			directly to request a new invitation.
		</p>
		<p style="margin-top: 2rem">Kind regards,<br />The iGreenMon Team</p>
	</body>
</html>
